ke":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"接放學啦。再跟就兇鳩條友<br />\n以前我都俾個女人跟過，我入七仔佢企門口等我<br />\n過兩日見到我又跟，真係好恐怖<br />\n之後有次我行到一半就即刻轉身同佢講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :&quot;跟撚夠未?&quot;<br />\n之後大喝一下佢就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fc099b0195889194c5588b2ffc627b7ebb06ef","tid":389893,"uid":5946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幫你接送<br />\n利申:180肌肉猛男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩個幫手接送，185高大運動形肥仔，唔嚇得都打得"},{"pid":"355ca17d48581151671ed4157ebba162c57e38b9","tid":389893,"uid":87771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:04:23.000Z","msg":"你叫幾個大隻fd一齊反跟蹤，問鳩佢做乜"},{"pid":"0e81a7fb1ff91daf07017bfd5c4598243def370f","tid":389893,"uid":7488,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:14:10.000Z","msg":"我可以護送妹妹返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 激情猛男"},{"pid":"f502ee4ad3521a0b70f9b2bc659c7ca265c143c0","tid":389893,"uid":43566,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:14:27.000Z","msg":"叫你阿妹係大街逛幾個圈，見到警就行埋去，行近先至同警講話後面條友跟左佢幾日。搞掂。<br />\n記得叫佢行大街。"},{"pid":"b84cf930258ba0021f7d228ebf5413036e1fa18d","tid":389893,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"送佢返學，一係叫佢改路線等佢跟唔到"},{"pid":"7539b47cffd0e4f6a1b1e0e7959733b29cb12b0a","tid":389893,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"好想保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9485b1c4c527deb040bfbeaf13306a6547ebb8b","tid":389893,"uid":79036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:05:39.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"207265c9f6e4592c461197eea6fd