d":389893,"uid":112467,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反跟蹤</blockquote><br />\n吊佢尾, 跟佢返屋企 約齊巴打上去開party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有party我黎湊人數<br />\n唔好影大合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7019e2b384d0c875f903d72285b725eda9aec7d","tid":389893,"uid":89949,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都扮跟你個妹<br />\n之後見到佢又跟 就搭下嗲<br />\n話呢個𡃁妹唔錯 自己跟左幾日 好想識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能咁樣可以chok到條友講佢個目的<br />\n過程錄埋音 再拎去報警</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條友跟得個女仔，九成都有壞意圖，唔通俾你chok兩句，佢會同你講想搞個女仔...再同樓主夾計做穴兄弟咩...咁做只會刺激佢。<br />\n<br />\n分分鍾條友已經有攻擊性武器係身，如果要現身兇條友，最好有多個伴一齊。"},{"pid":"b20ba6adbf44ff5f954babff703fd6a715087427","tid":389893,"uid":116247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:56:44.000Z","msg":"唔算靚女= 靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86803f3731c48954a259412acb92d7f6cbee3c3a","tid":389893,"uid":49998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"組隊接細妹放學"},{"pid":"3ac3d77194d2850f2bce243527d035f4118a42f4","tid":389893,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T19:03:17.000Z","msg":"解體保護佢囉問"},{"pid":"7d61ca31adc8730b61d9f36b1aeea7c011b1a21c","tid":389893,"uid":144295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T19:05:28.000Z","msg":"佢會慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4bd3bb8046667806ce8625691aa6d7bd959756","tid":389893,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T19:05:52.000Z","msg":"影低/拍片證明你個妹比人跟, 到時搵黑警做野都有D渣拿"},{"pid":"fa31464eaa66ca75ddf14a0e52110c3a1b62fef5","tid":389893,"uid":143945,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T19:23:44.000Z","msg":"邊區？<br />\n咩校服？<br />\n陣間幾十條油頭毒撚拉佢埋一邊訓話都幾撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\nbtw，巴打，<br />\n有 無 諗 過 其 實 跟 你 細 妹 嗰 個 人，<br />\n 都 睇 緊 哩 個 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"6daf5a1de4f84062ef12ef4223b04abd978e6b60","tid":389893,"uid":119017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T20:06:23.000Z","msg":"認真，你一定要搵人/自己接送妹妹，直至搵出d仆街，或者你同妹妹前後腳，傾住電話咁，因為隨時有人係你妹妹隔離條仆街唔出現。<br />\n<br />\n我樓下住著個有問題既人，同我同年，細個已經會成日走埋黎問我叫咩名，話我著錯校服etc，個陣佢係中學生都唔係好驚，最多佢行到好近個陣我跑走。中間去左外國幾年，返香港有次撞到佢，佢變到好高好肥好大舊，本身係大廈出面見到，佢跟到我入lift（臨關lift佢衝入黎），企到好埋好大聲話我著錯衫/問我好多古怪野，嚇撚到我仆街。最後我一出lift跑返屋企拍門大叫呀爸。"},{"pid":"de80819f93c29d9f4b59419175a6c6ae392afa6f","tid":389893,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T20:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>接放學啦。再跟就兇鳩條友<br />\n以前我都俾個女人跟過，我入七仔佢企門口等我<br />\n過兩日見到我又跟，真係好恐怖<br />\n之後有次我行到一半就即刻轉身同佢講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :&quot;跟撚夠未?&quot;<br />\n之後大喝一下佢就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n油塘？"},{"pid":"dfc50217d05e1633ec702a8d4ba637ef62f27b57","tid":389893,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁多次你阿妹都冇影佢相？</blockquote><br />\n認真問怕唔怕會刺激到佢 痴線佬痴起上嚟唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母男人老狗打得死你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a542888a3a8b1f16b1adde4faab4a03896dc9fa2","tid":389893,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T20:44:55.000Z","msg":"一陣變成班連登仔跟你個妹"},{"pid":"bfc2a3e0b2be3dc045bad3e858bbb3f53da66df9","tid":389893,"uid":28413,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T20:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊區？<br />\n咩校服？<br />\n陣間幾十條油頭毒撚拉佢埋一邊訓話都幾撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\nbtw，巴打，<br />\n有 無 諗 過 其 實 跟 你 細 妹 嗰 個 人，<br />\n 都 睇 緊 哩 個 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n唔通個個係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2561e01aa075070bfbf1fbdc39065b115ba67397","tid":389893,"uid":23423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T22:54:22.000Z","msg":"你要先知道真係有個人跟佢先<br />\n思覺失調都會有被害妄想"},{"pid":"77314725ffa7920664a41fabcafc6abbf913b957","tid":389893,"uid":50327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:04:15.000Z","msg":"好難證明條友係跟踪<br />\n香港無相應既法例<br />\n最多告佢遊蕩<br />\n黑警都做唔到d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：之前個女每朝返學都比個阿伯跟<br />\n兇完佢都係咁，報警都係咁，仲跟我全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433fd32ce2b7cdcc9f2451697166491129d1b4df","tid":389893,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我做阿妹保鏢唔收錢 要你阿妹電話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又知人地個妹唔係肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0a26edaecb868bbb8b2255639d01396e5fd253","tid":389893,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我做阿妹保鏢唔收錢 要你阿妹電話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又知人地個妹唔係肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主講呀妹有好多兵 應該唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d763beeed9359382c184e5668ea84403369413","tid":389893,"uid":42044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:24:34.000Z","msg":"邊度，我地跟返佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報警冇用，因為條友冇晌你妹身上做過嘢，黑警見倒條友都只係查下佢身份証，報警一次先會查一次，查完就放走。<br />\n<br />\n利申： 我姐試過"},{"pid":"04d1b9f6b8053d4ca09b7065dd9e571e830ce5c9","tid":389893,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:26:25.000Z","msg":"比阿妹張相我，等我可以保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0e41617d6fe1a8641afae755d2802777f7a1c6","tid":389893,"uid":770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我做阿妹保鏢唔收錢 要你阿妹電話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又知人地個妹唔係肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主講呀妹有好多兵 應該唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥婆都可以有兵 好似係"},{"pid":"c9be66084198cf0fe46bfd3c9783e8abf6e02e74","tid":389893,"uid":134335,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:30:48.000Z","msg":"很想跟你妹妹合體哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a17594c3b580a425fb9ebcbdd35c6728ff06c5f","tid":389893,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送佢返學，一係叫佢改路線等佢跟唔到</blockquote><br />\n佢有諗過行返學(一個站嘅距離) 但我覺得逼地鐵咁多人安全啲"},{"pid":"8c397a51213b43d2753198e08f90792b98485900","tid":389893,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:45:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁多次你阿妹都冇影佢相？</blockquote><br />\n認真問怕唔怕會刺激到佢 痴線佬痴起上嚟唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母男人老狗打得死你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我日日送就話唔驚姐 最弊我唔得嘛"},{"pid":"c05ab685eef8bfd70cea926301c9bccada7cb596","tid":389893,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>送佢返學，一係叫佢改路線等佢跟唔到</blockquote><br />\n佢有諗過行返學(一個站嘅距離) 但我覺得逼地鐵咁多人安全啲</blockquote><br />\n同埋跟蹤果條友一齊逼地鐵都幾安全吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭的士去學校門口落啦"},{"pid":"16986a1c661a6e02ee00f2df13737a6e56427868","tid":389893,"uid":71477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:57:35.000Z","msg":"改變返學路線囉<br />\n就算搭地鐵都可以唔同入口入<br />\n一日車頭，一日車尾，已經難跟好多啦<br />\n<br />\n最緊要提高危機意識<br />\n唔好去少人地方，有事要識大叫搵人幫手<br />\n聽落好似好簡單、好on9，但好多人遇事都係淆、縮"},{"pid":"eb1f5781a3aa19c92b139add4648ef934fa1ef79","tid":389893,"uid":69961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"早d出門口搭早一班車避開佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd27a96f7cb6e2fb95ac1157d07550cf968ffd54","tid":389893,"uid":76815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:05:40.000Z","msg":"係付近可以幫你<br />\n利申：190"},{"pid":"f5e31506b179e18d5f95ffb6a288de1e052d191c","tid":389893,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:07:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d39def29b1c035a6502262ea5085edfaa295f8b6","tid":389893,"uid":44916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你阿妹好快就進入青春期，比男人抱起黎屌！咁你做阿哥可以做到啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中六啦喎，重好快就？"},{"pid":"9cbf09fdb5a57c2d7e7e2ddaa2bcdd0260051d4a","tid":389893,"uid":108013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去睇下係咪跟 之後過去問佢咩事"},{"pid":"c38dd4550ad459453d99a8ae50eddcd2af67b2dc","tid":389893,"uid":45142,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:16:40.000Z","msg":"其實係親生老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142e4f2824a1fe66eb41664a426fba7b509053f5","tid":389893,"uid":61075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係親生老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5133585dc933739f3d6dadf6f9cfba5a7f51ed","tid":389893,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:45:25.000Z","msg":"真心你叫佢指俾我睇，我幫你搞掂件事<br />\n<br />\n請我食餐飯就ok"},{"pid":"eecc3da7ee6e88a82652bea93979de87cc9814f0","tid":389893,"uid":29764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:47:10.000Z","msg":"邊區"},{"pid":"b4560586bc0de810d02cf2112c2d727c82214b05","tid":389893,"uid":28402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:49:24.000Z","msg":"先確定係有呢條友存在先。<br />\n<br />\n搵幾日跟阿妹番學（請假都要），當然扮唔識阿妹，吊住佢尾就得。途中阿妹見到條痴漢，就message 你，你認9住佢個樣，反跟蹤佢。"},{"pid":"09d78bb6c6794429f71c593b28ec5a6760569182","tid":389893,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"最簡單係同學校老師講 如果有駐校副警仲方便<br />\n同埋仲有社工"},{"pid":"c73739a45d26d6d5f514f50934aff85e7d562460","tid":389893,"uid":139224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:46:06.000Z","msg":"好簡單，你黃雀在後跟佢咪得。"},{"pid":"854587d08fc3b268bb9df541081b226f9237cb2b","tid":389893,"uid":139224,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"我以前喺啲多廢老嘅區讀女校<br />\n周不時都有呢啲事<br />\n有次有個老野喺門口附近同我同學講淫野<br />\n啲阿sir收到風即刻落去圍鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4520a8428f7f9c05ac2c8f6e313ac1132ca9a669","tid":389893,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前喺啲多廢老嘅區讀女校<br />\n周不時都有呢啲事<br />\n有次有個老野喺門口附近同我同學講淫野<br />\n啲阿sir收到風即刻落去圍鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成班阿sir撚呀伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8847a7b44eb8b138ed1054115c9204f46995cc","tid":389893,"uid":83741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:19:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲人真係要屌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過比識既 但一啲都唔熟既人跟 最初係學校附近見到佢 仲同佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知去到係屋企樓下見到佢 又唔知係邊有我電話 就真係驚到瀨屎 <br />\n最後搵個男仔屌撚咗佢一鑊 從此消失"},{"pid":"ee30977f51043f8a16407b8a0a2e8a5460574aba","tid":389893,"uid":18587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:25:40.000Z","msg":"一陣百鳩幾人接樓主個妹放學，之後俾人拉撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f7713405f0a1f7a971d4a4688806dfbba4b7f1","tid":389893,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一陣百鳩幾人接樓主個妹放學，之後俾人拉撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多左百幾人跟蹤樓主個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ebd284115bf90d4333b045ed8c382ab1b4b8af","tid":389893,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我幫你接送<br />\n利申:180肌肉猛男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩個幫手接送，185高大運動形肥仔，唔嚇得都打得</blockquote><br />\n三個幫手接送，30cm高大猛男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a8e6e8f001d6a0d9ff4772b516d470712f8bc4","tid":389893,"uid":55747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反跟蹤</blockquote><br />\n睇完標題都諗到呢三個字，然後再起底"},{"pid":"a6bfe02d5beeb93e9063da88ba5b22674e23a77f","tid":389893,"uid":41888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:11:49.000Z","msg":"拿拿林反跟踪   <br />\n自己親身兇9條友啦<br />\n自己呀妹都同你講到出聲<br />\n你唔係想下一單強姦案主角係你呀妹下化?<br />\n跟踪時記得拍片做證據"},{"pid":"c9048d7d3a6a1d52752e8321ff3ccaf9822ab083","tid":389893,"uid":36380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7877c3837bcebe365bffdd2d936d92d0c631dfbc","tid":389893,"uid":39174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我幫你接送<br />\n利申:180肌肉猛男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩個幫手接送，185高大運動形肥仔，唔嚇得都打得</blockquote><br />\n樓主個妹到時仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa0266a9f48e82b8a56a8e33c21bb33575b2c4c","tid":389893,"uid":130897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"成堆連登仔整人牆圍住你個妹返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0f767852d2cca588fb3972e3de4c67d176348b","tid":389893,"uid":44504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco